    #[doc = " \\brief   Disable the I2C HW block\n  \\ingroup hardware_i2c\n\n \\param i2c Either \\ref i2c0 or \\ref i2c1\n\n Disable the I2C again if it is no longer used. Must be reinitialised before\n being used again."]
